  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/873c4bfc5b27e20c2b0d11c9af050f5f.webp?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=51 /></span>A relaxing tavern construction simulator for lovers of the Middle Ages and snowy locations. You manage your own tavern, you will not only need to build and arrange floors, walls and decorations, but also monitor various resources, manage the economy and balance between working buildings. You can create one huge tavern, or separate them and create many taverns on one map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/b4675c770dd917b8e27fc500b5ad4382.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/2170865b35d08d3c832bd99238575623.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/e410c8373fed1a07c6769f457ea40e1e.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You create the world yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Building structures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmosphere of the snowy biome</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Author's soundtracks from the developer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the game \"<i>Medieval simulators: Tavern</i>\" and enjoy the game. :)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/d6994abd6f836a0b8a2e3ba2430bb3f8.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/873c4bfc5b27e20c2b0d11c9af050f5f.webp?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=51 /></span>A relaxing tavern construction simulator for lovers of the Middle Ages and snowy locations. You manage your own tavern, you will not only need to build and arrange floors, walls and decorations, but also monitor various resources, manage the economy and balance between working buildings. You can create one huge tavern, or separate them and create many taverns on one map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/b4675c770dd917b8e27fc500b5ad4382.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/2170865b35d08d3c832bd99238575623.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/e410c8373fed1a07c6769f457ea40e1e.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You create the world yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Building structures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmosphere of the snowy biome</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Author's soundtracks from the developer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the game \"<i>Medieval simulators: Tavern</i>\" and enjoy the game. :)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437400/extras/d6994abd6f836a0b8a2e3ba2430bb3f8.avif?t=1769420309\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p>",
